    <h2 class="fw-bold">Think Nursing Career Think Jyoti</h2>
    <p class="text-muted fs-5">
        We offer a wide range of high-quality teaching and extra-curricular activities.
    </p>
    <p class="text-secondary">
         Jyoti Institute of Nursing and Technology is a reputed institute under 
         KIIT Deemed to be University, recognized by the Indian Nursing Council (INC) 
         and Odisha State Nursing Council since 2008. The college is committed to 
         delivering quality nursing education built on scientific principles and practical 
         training. It focuses on developing clinical competence, critical thinking, 
         and professional skills in students, preparing them to serve effectively across 
         various healthcare settings. With experienced faculty and a student-centered approach,
         the institute provides opportunities for academic growth, research, and a successful
         nursing career.
    </p>
    <hr class="mx-auto" style="width: 80px; border: 2px solid orange;">
</div>

